last_episode_to_air.name: The Next Wave
last_episode_to_air.overview: Tensions continue to run high when Sonya bails on everything Natalya had planned for their girls' trip, including fun surf lessons that end up going terribly wrong, sending Natalya, Liv Morgan and Sonya's girlfriend to the emergency room.

name: Total Divas
overview: An inside look of the lives of seven WWE Divas from their work within WWE to their personal lives.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Rosa Mendes joined the cast of Total Divas, as well as Alicia Fox and Paige; Naomi and Summer Rae departed as series regulars after the mid-season finale.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Naomi rejoined the cast while Cameron and Rosa Mendes depart as series regulars.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: Amanda Saccomanno joins the cast, as well as Rosa Mendes rejoining. Naomi departs as a series regular.

seasons.name: Season 7
seasons.overview: Season 7 of Total Divas premiered on November 1, 2017.

seasons.name: Season 9
seasons.overview: WWE stars Ronda Rousey and Sonya Deville join Natalya, Nia Jax and Trinity Fatu in the Queendom that empowers the WWE and the all-women's event Evolution.

episodes.name: A Tango with Fandango

episodes.name: Planet Funk is Funked Up
episodes.overview: Trinity & Jon Uso must face each other in the ring; Nikki is upset when Brie wants to move to Phoenix; JoJo's boyfriend gives her an ultimatum.

episodes.name: The 'Fat' Twin
episodes.overview: Nikki is insecure about her weight; Ariane considers getting breast implants; Natalya wants more romance from her fiancé, TJ.

episodes.name: Feuding Funkadactyls
episodes.overview: Trinity & Ariane's conflict escalates; the Bellas & JoJo reunite with their estranged fathers; Jaret, confesses feelings for Nattie.

episodes.name: Diva Las Vegas
episodes.overview: The Divas & several WWE superstars go to Vegas for Nattie's bachelorette party; JoJo's is warned against dating a much older Justin Gabriel; Ariane is upset with Nattie.

episodes.name: A Leg Up

episodes.name: Get That Chingle Chingle
episodes.overview: Ariane forces Vincent to try out for WWE; Nikki struggles to feel comfortable in John Cena's home; Trinity and Jon's relationship changes.

episodes.name: Saying Goodbye
episodes.overview: Nattie and TJ must put their pet to sleep; Trinity and Jon come to blows over his jealous behavior; tension grows between Brie and Nikki.

episodes.name: Ready to Ride
episodes.overview: Bryan proposes to Brie; Nikki and John Cena's future is uncertain; Eva Marie introduces her fiancé to her family.

episodes.name: New Diva On The Block
episodes.overview: Nikki faces a life without her boyfriend; Summer Rae joins the main roster; Eva Marie faces her parents.

episodes.name: The Braniel Bus
episodes.overview: Brie convinces Daniel Bryan to get a tour bus; Eva Marie is embarrassed when her past is exposed; Nikki loses a tooth.

episodes.name: On Brie's Bad Side
episodes.overview: When Summer Rae flirts with Daniel Bryan, Brie becomes her enemy; Nattie's feud escalates.

episodes.name: Inhale, Exhale
episodes.overview: Nattie faces surgery after injury; Nikki suspects John Cena of lying; Trinity makes a music video.

episodes.name: For Better or For Worse
episodes.overview: Trinity wants to get married; Eva faces a serious health issue; Nikki and Ariane help Nattie get her groove back.

episodes.name: The House Sitters
episodes.overview: Ariane throws a party and loses Nattie's cat; Nattie and T.J. clash over money; Brie educates Nikki about food.

episodes.name: Flirting With Fandango
episodes.overview: Trinity wants to get married but not without Jon's father's blessing; Eva faces a serious health issue; Nikki and Ariane help Nattie get her groove back.

episodes.name: Red and Gold
episodes.overview: Eva Marie and Summer Rae battle outside the ring; Ariane takes it too far when trying to become famous; Nattie shows her artistic side.

episodes.name: What Happens In Cabo
episodes.overview: At Brie's bachelorette party in Mexico, Eva Marie struggles with her sobriety; Nikki reveals a secret from her past; Trinity suffers an eye injury.

episodes.name: Digging A Hole
episodes.overview: The Bella sisters clash as Brie's wedding fast approaches; Nikki avoids telling John about her previous marriage.

episodes.name: Wedding Mania
episodes.overview: Brie and Bryan get married; Nikki's secret marriage is finally exposed; WrestleMania.

episodes.name: Eggs Over Freezing
episodes.overview: Brie is left helpless when Bryan's injury takes a turn for the worst. Meanwhile, Ariane's mother calls with a desperate plea for help, and Eva is shocked when Jonathan makes a dangerous decision without her consent.

episodes.name: Mo' Marriage, Mo' Problems
episodes.overview: Brie regrets quarreling with her husband when he delivers devastating news; Nikki's secret has John fearing the end of their relationship, and Trinity is blindsided when Ariane puts the future of the Funkadactyls at risk.

episodes.name: Roadside Rumble
episodes.overview: Brie and Bryan's wrestling careers are at risk; Brie's effort to save their future puts Nikki in a tough spot with John; Rosa fails at reconciling two enemies.

episodes.name: Divas Unchained
episodes.overview: Nattie is hit on by colleague while taking a break from TJ; Bryan and Nikki team up and stage an intervention.

episodes.name: Scared Straight
episodes.overview: Brie is left helpless when Bryan's injury takes a turn for the worst. Meanwhile, Ariane's mother calls with a desperate plea for help, and Eva is shocked when Jonathan makes a dangerous decision without her consent.

episodes.name: Paint the Island Red
episodes.overview: Eva's sexy bachelorette in Curacao gets heated when TJ destroys Nattie's hopes of rekindling their marriage, Nikki believes she's lost her twin sister, and Ariane kicks Vinnie's desires to the curb.

episodes.name: The Double Cross
episodes.overview: Nikki is devastated when she discovers John's kept a secret from her. Meanwhile, Rosa's unaware she's competing in her pursuits of an NFL player, and Nattie's unsavory comments to a reporter cause TJ to take an extreme action.

episodes.name: Cross Country Catastrophe
episodes.overview: Things spiral out of control when Rosa finds Summer with her man; Brie learns that Bryan is keeping tabs on her.

episodes.name: Daddy's Little Girl
episodes.overview: Eva lashes out as she comes to terms with her Dad's terminal cancer; Nattie and TJ face the cruel realities of getting a divorce.

episodes.name: The Divas Are Taking Over
episodes.overview: Brie goes behind John's back and confronts Nikki leading to explosive consequences; the truth about Nattie's marriage is revealed to the Divas.

episodes.name: Her Highness
episodes.overview: The Bella family erupts when Nikki discovers the truth about John; a member of UK wrestling royalty, Paige, takes the Divas division by storm.

episodes.name: Baby Not on Board
episodes.overview: Eva springs something on Jonathan that she should have disclosed before marriage; Nikki cuts off the Bella family; Rosa's job is threatened.

episodes.name: Twin Leaks
episodes.overview: Eva faces a life-threatening medical issue; Paige gets a tad too close to Nattie in the ring, and a friendly competition between Nikki and John turns into a serious throw-down.

episodes.name: Insecurity Breach
episodes.overview: Ariane goes behind Eva's back and gets together with Jonathan to confront Eva Marie about a major issue; Brie is afraid of retaliation after her house is broken into; Paige faces the consequences of sending mixed signals.

episodes.name: Girl Vs. Girl Bye
episodes.overview: Brie confesses that she doesn't use protection, which could be the end of the Bella twins; Nattie is has to to work with TJ regardless of their separation; Ariane's attempt to find out why Alicia hates her ends in a disaster.

episodes.name: All Hail Brie Mode
episodes.overview: Brie and Paige take the UK by storm causing Nikki to worry that Brie's extreme behavior will jeopardize their performance in the ring; Nattie asks TJ for help with a family disaster and Alicia falls apart when confronted with her ex-boyfriend.

episodes.name: Mo' Money, Mo' Purses
episodes.overview: Nattie takes on the task of renovating her mom's house; Brie attempts to curb Nicole's out of control spending, and Eva Marie makes a Vegas bucket list for her Dad when she fears the worst for his health.

episodes.name: Model Behavior
episodes.overview: Ariane is embarrassed to have her father to meet Vinnie's family; Nattie struggles to support TJ's new career choice when he strips down with some hot models; Paige rebels when WWE tells her not to get a tattoo.

episodes.name: Indecent Exposure
episodes.overview: Paige brings her new hookup to a Three Amigas vacation in Key West; the Bellas are startled by a nude pic of their brother; Nattie meets Grumpy Cat.

episodes.name: The New Divas Champion
episodes.overview: The Bellas think about signing on for another three years in the ring; Paige asks Bradley to move to LA before realizing there are skeletons in his closet; Eva's husband risks her relationship with the WWE.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Rosa Mendes joined the cast of Total Divas, as well as Alicia Fox and Paige; Naomi and Summer Rae departed as series regulars after the mid-season finale.

episodes.name: Diva Divide
episodes.overview: The Bellas face the consequences of leaving the WWE; news of Eva's new role creates chaos in the Divas division; Nattie explores her dominatrix side.

episodes.name: She Said, She Said
episodes.overview: WrestleMania week has a rocky start. Brie is concerned that she and Bryan are having fertility issues.

episodes.name: Eat Your Heart Out
episodes.overview: Nikki and Eva's peace talks end badly. Nattie takes a chance on stage.

episodes.name: Divas on Overdrive
episodes.overview: Paige ditches Alicia for a new man; Nattie can't give no for an answer and ends up infuriating her husband; Nikki challenges Bryan over not liking her.

episodes.name: Tea Mode
episodes.overview: Alicia, anticipating that her ex-boyfriend may be single again soon, toys with the idea of confessing her love to him; Jonathan takes heat for Eva's bruises; and Paige is offended by Nikki's classy take on her home turf.

episodes.name: Good Diva, Bad Diva
episodes.overview: Nattie is caught in a web of lies after she invites her sister to move in with her; Nikkie is concerned that Brie isn't taking Bryan's health seriously enough; and Trinity's future hinges on her inner bad girl.

episodes.name: No Holds Barre
episodes.overview: JJ tries to take over the twins' new business, causing great deals of tension in the Bella family; Trinity proves herself as a step-mother; Eva tries to prove herself to the Divas with a risky move she has planned out for herself.

episodes.name: It's a Beautiful Life?
episodes.overview: Brie sets Nikki up to make her national debut as a vocalist when she claims that she is the better singer; Paige tests Kevin in order to address her trust issues; Nattie worries that the WWE is phasing her out, so she takes drastic actions.

episodes.name: Clash of the Divas
episodes.overview: Paige lands herself in hot water with the WWE; Nattie sets her sister up with Big E; and Bryan takes issue with Brie's new sexy wardrobe.

episodes.name: Gone with the Wine
episodes.overview: Nikki goes to Napa for some much-needed relaxation; Trinity takes her less-than-enthusiastic family on a camping trip in an R.V.; much to her displeasure, Eva finds herself forced to choose between her career and Jonathan.

episodes.name: An Unwanted Proposal
episodes.overview: A marriage proposal catches Paige completely out of the blue; Bryan has plans for his future, but Brie doesn't see eye to eye with him about them, causing conflict; Trinity's plans for Jon's career in standup comedy go terribly wrong.

episodes.name: Some Like It Hot
episodes.overview: While enjoying a group vacation in distant Tulum, Mexico, Paige makes the announcement that she is engaged, the Bellas learn that they are going to have a new sibling and Alicia endangers Trinity's relationship with Jon.

episodes.name: Return of the Ex
episodes.overview: The heat is turned up by Nikki's ex-boyfriend; Nattie tries to deal with career-ending news that will affect both herself and TJ; Paige can't decide if she should tell her fiancé how she really feels or not, and she debates her course of action.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: Naomi rejoined the cast while Cameron and Rosa Mendes depart as series regulars.

episodes.name: Love Triangle
episodes.overview: Nikki is unsure about telling John Cena about her ex-boyfriend's advances; Paige feels the pressure to call off her engagement; Brie tries to pave a new career path for Bryan.

episodes.name: A SummerSlam Engagement
episodes.overview: Nattie's worst fears come true when she is left out of SummerSlam; Alicia feels disrespected by her best friend Paige; John Cena surprises Nikki with news that he is finally open to marriage.

episodes.name: The Truth About Cats and Divas
episodes.overview: Eva Marie makes her much-anticipated return to the Diva Division and a newcomer joins the Diva ranks; Nattie hosts a Superstar surprise party for TJ in order to cheer him up; the Bellas have a disagreement over signing an endorsement.

episodes.name: Talk of the Town
episodes.overview: Nikki is inspired by Maria Shriver to become a motivational speaker, but Brie ridicules her for it; Paige and Rosa attempt to cheer up Alicia when she finds out her new boyfriend is lying to her; Mandy wonders if her alliance with Eva is a mistake.

episodes.name: Come Reign or Shine
episodes.overview: Brie and Nikki argue as Brie questions her risking the chance of a potential injury for the chance to be the longest Diva Champion of all time; Alicia and Rosa argue over the vision of Rosa's baby shower; Nattie questions how serious Mandy is.

episodes.name: End of A Friendship?
episodes.overview: Brie drives her sister away when she refuses to facilitate Nikki's worries of being alone; Rosa is worried about her religious mother meeting her boyfriend who is an atheist; Alicia Fox is thinking about ending her friendship with Paige.

episodes.name: Hart of the Matter
episodes.overview: Nikki's chances of holding the title are in jeopardy when she faces an old opponent; Nattie is not sure to take TJ's last name or have him take hers; Paige has relationship problems; Brie has a bone to pick with Byran; Rosa tries to find a purpose.

episodes.name: Peace of Cake
episodes.overview: Paige hides a lie from her mother, and the decision to do that then causes the end of her relationship with her boyfriend; Nikki is worried about Brie's safety after she makes a dangerous purchase; Rosa accuses Bobby of him food shaming her.

episodes.name: Rocky Road To Recovery
episodes.overview: Nikki gets John to be her rehab coach, but she mixes business and pleasure too much with her rehab; Rosa is suspicious of Bobby when he goes to Las Vegas without her; Nattie struggles to get her family together for a portrait of the family.

episodes.name: No Retreat
episodes.overview: Paige gets cold feet after agreeing to help a fan come out to his family; Brie is torn between her friends and Bryan; Eva has to form a tag team with rookie Mandy Rose.

episodes.name: Clothes Quarters
episodes.overview: Brie's stubbornness forms a roadblock for the Bella's new lingerie line; Mandy is on a mission to reconnect her parents while on a joint family vacation with the Neidharts; Nattie attempts to suppress her dad's embarrassing antics.

episodes.name: Baby Talk
episodes.overview: Paige is haunted by a painful memory of her past, as Rosa's baby shower approaches; Nikki is determined to prove that she can hang with Brie and Bryan in the wilderness; Alicia is anxious to find a way to fix her family's issues.

episodes.name: C'est La Diva (1)
episodes.overview: The Divas set off for Paris where one Diva gets the proposal of a lifetime; relationships start to crumble as the tension between Fox and Rosa peaks; Eva ditches Mandy to hang out with the Bellas.

episodes.name: C'est La Diva (2)
episodes.overview: The Divas' Paris getaway continues, as the divide between the Divas gets bigger; Rosa finally meets her little bundle of joy; Nikki learns the fate of her career with WWE.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: Amanda Saccomanno joins the cast, as well as Rosa Mendes rejoining. Naomi departs as a series regular.

episodes.name: Total Superstars
episodes.overview: A secret from Brie's past is revealed, Lana makes her debut at Wrestlemania, Trinity suffers a hair disaster, and the WWE has a major announcement about the future of the women's division.

episodes.name: Orlando Strong
episodes.overview: Trinity goes to Orlando to honor victims of the Pulse Nightclub shooting, Nikki accuses Brie of sweeping Bryan's depression under the rug while Lana annoys Nattie before the championship.

episodes.name: A Big Flippin' Deal
episodes.overview: Maryse clashes with Mike when she makes big decisions without him, Brie has a pregnancy scare and Trinity is offered a role in Marine 5 but must face her fears of riding a motorcycle first.

episodes.name: Gone Girl
episodes.overview: Renee must intervene after Paige behaves erratically and misses work, and Nikki asks Bryan to help with her comeback against Brie's wishes.

episodes.name: Mother of the Groom
episodes.overview: Maryse and Mike’s home is invaded. Lana, Rusev and his mother argue over wedding locations, and Renee has a meltdown when the Bellas visit her and Dean Ambrose in Vegas for the first time.

episodes.name: Too Many Cooks
episodes.overview: Brie challenges Nikki to an I.Q. test, Trinity battles nerves on a movie set, Nattie pushes her sister too hard on a new cooking school, and Lana and Rusev fight over engagement photos.

episodes.name: A Win-Wine Situation
episodes.overview: Paige blows up at Eva when she suspects she outed her neck injury. Nikki wants to start a winery, but Brie doesn't take her seriously. Nattie's wrestling character has to turn 'bad.’

episodes.name: Pain in the Neck
episodes.overview: Bryan gets a job offer that may interfere with Brie’s plans to start a family and Paige gets MRI results. Nattie wants out of planning Lana’s wedding and Renee third wheels a couples’ trip.

episodes.name: What Happens in Vegas
episodes.overview: Lana’s bachelorette Vegas trip brings up questions of her upcoming wedding to Rusev. Nikki’s nerves get the best of her when her family walks the red carpet as John Cena hosts the ESPYS’.

episodes.name: The Big Day
episodes.overview: Renee brings Dean Ambrose home to meet her family, Lana and Rusev’s wedding day arrives and last minute disagreements heighten emotions. Nikki finds out if she's cleared for the WWE draft.

episodes.name: The Draft
episodes.overview: The WWE draft is finally here and the superstars await the outcome, which could affect their relationships. Nikki is determined to get drafted, and asks Nattie to train with her in the ring.

episodes.name: Feel the Glow
episodes.overview: Maryse and Eva come to blows over a photo shoot. Renee and Dean Ambrose go on vacation but can't find the romance. Retired Brie goes back on the road and Trinity pitches a new character.

episodes.name: Group-Sext
episodes.overview: Trinity and Renee get fed up with Lana while in the Caribbean and a fight ensues. Maryse accidentally sends a nude selfie and Brie debates if she wants to have a kid if she has to eat meat.

episodes.name: Runaway Bride
episodes.overview: During their wedding, Rusev pushes Lana outside of her comfort zone. Nicole gets an offer to go on “Dancing With the Stars” and wonders if she should quit WWE. Eva Marie pushes a healthier lifestyle on her sick father.

episodes.name: Swimming With Pigs
episodes.overview: Forced to retire her signature move, the Rack Attack, Nicole struggles to find her new identity as a WWE superstar. Maryse and Eva take their hubbies on a joint, sexy honeymoon trip to Exuma. Nattie crashes a meeting with the Bellas' pet agency, sparking a pet war.

episodes.name: Total Summerslam
episodes.overview: The Superstars take New York by storm during Summerslam week. Nicole comes to terms with not being able to make the comeback of her dreams. Summer Slam gets thrown into disarray when Eva becomes suspended days before the event.

episodes.name: This Is Make or Break
episodes.overview: The women's division gets their first ever Money in the Bank ladder match; Nicole strives to become SmackDown Live's General Manager by mentoring Lana and Nattie, and Nia leaves a bad taste in Maryse's after she asks a bold question.

episodes.name: Dressed Like A Champ
episodes.overview: The ladies celebrate the success of their historic ladder match, but Lana's performance suffers intense scrutiny; Maryse's fashion makeover triggers Alexa's painful past; Nattie, who hates babies, is tasked to babysit Brie's newborn.

episodes.name: Breaking All The Rules
episodes.overview: Trinity goes behind WWE's back and alters her championship in order to give it a glow; Lana pulls a stunt by posting a photo that could get her fired; Brie recruits Nikki to go on a road trip to San Diego with a breastfeeding infant in the car.

episodes.name: The Diva Divide
episodes.overview: A fight breaks out between Lana, Nattie and Nia when their critique of each other's wrestling skills becomes too personal; a third home robbery makes Maryse want to move; Brie begins donating her breast milk to babies in need.

episodes.name: Bella Rush
episodes.overview: Lana hosts a Bulgarian Name's Day party for Resev in Nashville, but she isn't prepared to give him the present he really wants; Nattie buys her parents a house but soon realizes they're awful tenants; the Bellas try to find a new adrenaline rush.

episodes.name: Divas Gone Wild
episodes.overview: Brie struggles to enjoy herself on her first vacation away from her newborn, but Brie Mode eventually makes a return; the tension between Nattie and Lana reaches a climax and threatens to ruin everyone's time.

episodes.name: Fake It 'Til You Make It
episodes.overview: After surviving her first trip away from Birdie, Brie becomes inspired to make a comeback in the ring and in her business career; Trin introduces role-playing in the bedroom to spice up her sex life; Maryse dares Mike to be a vegetarian for a week.

episodes.name: Single in the City
episodes.overview: Nia confronts Alexa on her sketchy wedding plans and ruins the fun; Lana's physical affection for women pushes Rusev to his limit as a husband; Carmella confronts Lana for messing with her career.

episodes.name: Three Alarm Fire
episodes.overview: Nia faces her fears and braves a date with a NYC firefighter; Lana's criticism of Nattie's skills on the mic gets in Nattie's head before her big SummerSlam match, forcing Nattie to do something drastic.

7.name: Season 7
7.overview: Season 7 of Total Divas premiered on November 1, 2017.

episodes.name: This Is My House
episodes.overview: WrestleMania 34 starts with a bang as the Bellas support and watch Trinity, Nattie and Lana compete in the first Women's Battle Royal; Nia's anxiety goes into overdrive before her championship match; Paige comes to terms with her retirement.

episodes.name: The Real Nicole
episodes.overview: Nicole escapes to Palm Springs with Brie to gain clarity and focus on her independence; Nattie has a humiliating wardrobe malfunction just as she starts a storyline with Ronda Rousey; Jon attempts to fix Trinity's sweet tooth but fails miserably.

episodes.name: Paige's Secret
episodes.overview: Paige is faced with coming clean with a big secret she's been keeping from everyone; Nattie tries to convince everyone that she is the "hostess with the mostest," but can't even get food on the table; Brie is faced with mom guilt.

episodes.name: Pink Hair Don't Care
episodes.overview: Nia invites Nattie, Trinity and Lana over to celebrate her new home; Lana is concerned with reinventing her character in the WWE to stay relevant but she takes it to drastic measures; Nicole and Brie take Paige out to blow off some steam.

episodes.name: Welcome to Miami
episodes.overview: The WWE Female Superstars head to Miami to celebrate Nattie and Nia's birthday with surprises in store; Nicole is hounded by the paparazzi even when flirting with a hot bartender; the Superstars' dancing skills are put to the test.

episodes.name: Chase Your Dreams
episodes.overview: Lana seeks advice from Brie and Nicole when Rusev announces he wants to have a baby; Nicole goes against Brie's wishes and plans a surprise party with Rusev for Birdie's first birthday.

episodes.name: Hate Is a Strong Word
episodes.overview: A girls bonding trip to Lake Tahoe quickly escalates into a heated fight between Lana and Paige; Trinity catches up with family and friends in Atlanta without Jon.

episodes.name: A Sisterhood Beyond Blood
episodes.overview: After a rocky first night, Trinity joins the Bellas, Nattie, Nia, Paige and Lana in Tahoe, where they bond in a way they never have before; Brie tries to convince the girls that the lake monster Tahoe Tessy is indeed real.

episodes.name: Unbreakable Force
episodes.overview: Historic Money in the Bank match; Nia prepares for her match against Ronda Rousey; Trinity tries to get her relationship with Jon back on track; Nattie and her family are faced with the loss of her father, Jim 'The Anvil' Neidhart.

episodes.name: The Baddest Women on the Planet
episodes.overview: Ronda Rousey makes her debut. Ronda struggles with the pressures of when she's going to be a mother and put her career on hold. Nia lets her true feelings out on Carmella before a huge match at Royal Rumble, leaving Carmella in tears.

episodes.name: All Is Fair In Love and War
episodes.overview: Carmella's new relationship is exposed and implicated as an affair. Sonya wins back her ex-girlfriend just in time to celebrate Pride where Sonya will be featured on her very own float. Natalya seeks to live on in her dad's legacy.

episodes.name: Rowdy Ronda
episodes.overview: Ronda Rousey invites Natalya to enjoy the simple life on her farm; Sonya attempts to start a feud with Ronda; Trinity performs in an underwater mermaid show; Carmella invites her new boyfriend, Corey Graves, to her 80s themed housewarming party.

episodes.name: Damage Control
episodes.overview: Tensions run high as Ronda Rousey makes bold moves to shake up the women's division. Trinity steps up to host her first ever girls' trip to Florida. Carmella visits Corey's hometown for the first time since their relationship was exposed.

episodes.name: The Real Ronda
episodes.overview: After Ronda Rousey posts an explosive video on social media which upsets the other female Superstars, Ronda must find a way to prove that she's not the villain she's made out to be. Sonya worries her relationship is moving way too fast.

episodes.name: Mountainmania
episodes.overview: Worried she's not welcome in the locker room, Ronda Rousey invites the female superstars to her mountain cabin for some much-needed bonding time. Sonya turns every activity into a heated competition. Carmella sneaks away with her boyfriend.

episodes.name: I Will Prevail
episodes.overview: With WrestleMania just around the corner, Sonya learns she will be making history with the first LGBTQ storyline. Natalya vies for her first WrestleMania moment in an attempt to honor her late father and the legacy he left behind.

episodes.name: 35 Years in the Making
episodes.overview: In the first WrestleMania headlined by women, Ronda gives everything she has in what could be her last match; the Bellas wonder if it's their time to come back as a tag-team; Natalya prepares to give the ultimate tribute to her father.

episodes.name: Hawaiian Punch
episodes.overview: After her last match with WWE, Ronda is excited to move on and start trying for a baby with her husband, Travis Browne.

episodes.name: The Next Wave
episodes.overview: Tensions continue to run high when Sonya bails on everything Natalya had planned for their girls' trip, including fun surf lessons that end up going terribly wrong, sending Natalya, Liv Morgan and Sonya's girlfriend to the emergency room.

9.name: Season 9
9.overview: WWE stars Ronda Rousey and Sonya Deville join Natalya, Nia Jax and Trinity Fatu in the Queendom that empowers the WWE and the all-women's event Evolution.
